parameters: \n<\n[1]>Hmm...? Wanz...? Are you in the restroom...?
\n<???>Attack!!! It's an attack!!! Monsters are assaulting us!!!

parameters.name: ダンジョン7(アンデッドタワー)170121_147bpm

parameters:
\n<Innkeeper>"What's this? Monsters are attacking? Is this how the town
ends? Pathetic, isn't it."

\n<Innkeeper>"Huh? One of the twins? I don't know. I might have seen
them, but I don't remember now. How many beers do you think
I've had?"

\n<Innkeeper>I've had enough. I've lived a long life. It was a pointless
life anyway. Might as well get eaten by monsters.

\n<Innkeeper>You better run fast. Even an old hag's flesh has some good
bits to eat. I'll buy you some time.

\n<Old Man>Hey, don't just barge in here, cat. I'm too tired to care
anymore, just leave it be. There's nowhere to run anyway.

\n<Old Man>Whether I get eaten by monsters or die of alcoholism, it's
all the same in the end.

\n<Old Man>Anything in the room, if you can use it, take it. I don't
need it anymore. See ya, cat.

\n<Peddler>Good grief. This is what happens during my drinking time.
What a hassle this has become. You're going to fight, aren't
you? Huh.

\n<Peddler>Money? Of course, I'm taking it. I'm a merchant until I die.
When I'm dead, you can take it all. But don't kill me, okay?
